{"tid":1564420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[核彈變宇宙兵器] 發動在美港人同香港人同步越洋合唱美國國歌","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T18:29:25.000Z","uid":35776,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb33804aec570f13011c91c77e6cbb406cab4fa","tid":1564420,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"如果熱青城屌人功夫分D落同人合作同諗計升級變招就好, 最衰佢哋諗點樣升級前鐘意唔同意就屌左人先，多過諗互相補位<br />\n<br />\n如題 此計預計有3part 練習 熱身 總攻<br />\n<br />\n請在美香港手足同香港手足共同約定時間<br />\n<br />\n合唱the star spangled banner <br />\n<br />\n熱身日子：跟住嘅集會日子擇一 但總攻一定係929,10.1 呢兩個日子<br />\n集合地點：各自洲份嘅最大城市一齊唱 (盡量邀請埋關注香港嘅美國愛國者一齊合唱 壯大隊伍 ) 香港同紐約可以係時代廣場<br />\n時間最好 香港上午美國下午(香港人冇咁早醒sor)<br />\n依家有人提議練住歌先 ok fine <br />\n但10.1 前任意集會當中 最好有一次預演<br />\n然後10.1當日發動總攻 舉旗 唱歌(未撚夠七點好出去，早撚過佢扯旗，撞埋時間仲好) <br />\n<br />\n呢個plan直頭滿足晒大部份人嘅要求<br />\n和而不同(除左港共之外<br />\n<br />\n而美國以外嘅外國手足同樣可以集合，但唱god save the queen, 拉完美國同時拉英國，一石二鳥"},{"pid":"9db23b74b4ce88922b7359a30af81960d4370b9c","tid":1564420,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QV6Mycc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV6Mycc.jpg&h=35dfaea1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d51dac6fc180bfd115016e3bcec09308aa27b915","tid":1564420,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REHv0jX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREHv0jX.png&h=4961a981&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSVp4MD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSVp4MD.jpg&h=3d25b08e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvwgVTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvwgVTi.jpg&h=88868b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZxWVTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\